[/size][/color][color=#00ff00][size=5]
[/size][/color]Teleport stone is near stable outside whiterun, look for the sign post and you will see the portal stone on the right to teleport to NIFlHEIM


I have only posted a few pics how to get to NIFlHEIM, the fun is to discover NIFlHEIM for yourself.


There are some npc,s there i have done my best to get rid of the black face bug (ctrl+F4 when in S,C,Kit)so if you get the black face bug this could be due to one of your mods.


You can post your pics and your video,s with my full conscent if you so wish.


If you encounter any probles with the mod uninstall it im taking a break from modding.

[color=#00ff00]Thank you to the community that supported my other mods by endosing them.[/color]


Requirements:          Dawnguard.Hearthfire.Dragonborn.Installation:         
                                  Just download with Nexus mod manger, Mod organizer or manual,if you want to install it manually,                                                                                             then you have to extract it into your data file for Skyrim.

Unistallation:         Just untick in mod manger or mod organzier or delete the files you manually installed.
